    <abstract id="aspace_ref10">Brooklynite Ina Clausen co-founded a women's collective print shop in the late 1960s. This collection consists of her personal papers as well as records from the Greenpoint Print Shop and copies of feminist writings and publications to which Clausen contributed.</abstract>
